\v 3 Ngitsho amakhanka\x + Hlab. 74.13.\x* ehlisa ibele, amunyise imidlwane yawo; \add kodwa\add* indodakazi yabantu bami isilesihluku\x + Jobe 30.21.\x*, njengezintshe\x + Jobe 30.29; Jobe 39.13-17.\x* enkangala.
\v 4 Ulimi lomunyayo lunamathela\x + Hlab. 22.15.\x* olwangeni lwakhe ngenxa yokoma; abantwanyana\x + Lilo 2.11,12; 1.11.\x* bacela isinkwa, kakho obahlephulelayo\x + Mika 3.3.\x*.
